room_title: Escape room "Sweet Revenge" by Just Escape in New York
room_description: Wouldn’t it be great to never grow up? We need your help in the search for the fountain of youth! Obsessed with youth and imagination, Dr. Dylan has developed a truly sweet recipe for everlasting youth in his candy store but doesn’t want to share it with anyone. You have access to his amazing candy store for just one hour while Dr. Dylan is out. Can you find the secret recipe before he gets back?
